<h1>Augmented Reality: Toolkit</h1>
<h2>ARKit</h2>
<p>
  ARKit, a powerful augmented reality framework provided by Apple, allowed me to place virtual content 
  at tracked, real-world locations within my apartment. Once placed, ARKit provided the hand gestures necessary 
  to interact with and scale the virtual content. Ultimately, by using world tracking and ray casting, ARKit convincingly 
  arranged virtual models in my world space and made for a realistic augmented reality experience.
</p>
